scene.message:
Maki: Chisato! Yosuke!{nl}
Thank goodness{nl}
you're safe!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, Naito.{nl}
What happened to the school?{nl}
There's nobody but you guys.{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: I don't know.{nl}
When we came back,{nl}
there was no one left.{waitkey}{clearbox}The east half of town{nl}
vanished too. I'm the one{nl}
who wants to know what's{nl}
going on.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I'm sorry... Chisato,{nl}
Yosuke. It's all my fault...{nl}
This is what it all was...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I promise I'll send{nl}
everyone back to the{nl}
original world for sure.{waitkey}{clearbox}No amount of apology{nl}
can make up for it, but...{nl}
I'm truly sorry.{waitkey}Hit me till you feel{nl}
better, Chisato.{waitkey}{ret}

Chisato: You dummy, Maki!{nl}
You really are so clumsy.{nl}
You always were...{waitkey}{ret}

Chisato: I'm the one who{nl}
should apologize...{waitkey}{clearbox}You called me here because{nl}
you thought of me as{nl}
your best friend, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}And I betrayed a Maki{nl}
like that. I'm the one who{nl}
needs forgiveness...{waitkey}It's the other way around.{waitkey}{ret}

Chisato: Now, off you go.{nl}
I'll wait here so I won't{nl}
be a burden.{waitkey}{clearbox}When it's all settled...{nl}
let's all go to the{nl}
amusement park, okay Maki?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh... amusement park.{nl}
Being a kid again ain't bad.{nl}
C'mon, let's wrap this up!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Beyond this door is{nl}
the worst version of me...{nl}
I can't lose. Not ever!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...This is the{nl}
home stretch.{nl}
Let's bring it, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Come to think of it,{nl}
that compact... may symbolize{nl}
the three primary colors{nl}
of light.{waitkey}The human heart can{nl}
become any color.{waitkey}{clearbox}Which color it takes is{nl}
up to oneself... Perhaps{nl}
that's what it means.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Get going.{nl}
I'll deal with all the{nl}
small fry myself.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: This is it at last...{nl}
Let's finish quickly and{nl}
go to the park together.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: This is it.{nl}
Let's finish quickly and{nl}
go to the park together!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'd love to ride the{nl}
ferris wheel with you,{nl}
{ctl07:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: My blood's pumping!{waitkey}Anyone who gets in my way{nl}
gets a taste of my Persona{nl}
Wonderful Bomber!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Amusement park, huh.{nl}
Ayase wants the Free Fall!{nl}
I did five in a row before.{waitkey}{clearbox}Next is ten in a row!{nl}
And of course you're{nl}
coming with me, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Amusement park, huh.{nl}
Ayase wants the Free Fall!{nl}
I did five in a row before.{waitkey}{clearbox}Next is ten in a row!{nl}
And of course {ctl08:8961}{nl}
is coming with me!{waitkey}{ret}

Chisato: Take care.{nl}
But... you're quite the{nl}
sly one too, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}One look at Maki's face{nl}
and I can tell at once{nl}
who she likes now.{waitkey}{ret}

Chisato: Take care.{nl}
But... you're quite the{nl}
sly one too, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}One look at Maki's face{nl}
and I can tell at once{nl}
who she likes now.{waitkey}And what's more...{waitkey}{clearbox}it doesn't seem to be{nl}
just Maki... You may be in{nl}
for a rough time, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Do your best.{nl}
I can't be of any help,{nl}
but I'm rooting for you.{waitkey}{ret}
